I was seated at the room's center, behind a grand, antique desk of dark mahogany, its surface cleared except for a single, neatly arranged stack of papers.

LineNo: 12399339,

en


I entered the grand reception hall to make my address to the nation speech.

LineNo: 12399441,

en


The hall, usually echoing with the rare footsteps of courtiers, was transformed into a noisy chaos, as the filming crew set up cameras, lights and microphones in place.

LineNo: 12401707,

Player_Romus: My loyal subjects...
en


"My loyal subjects..."

LineNo: 12401809,

Player_Romus: My esteemed countrymen and women...
en


"My esteemed countrymen and women..."

LineNo: 12401911,

Player_Romus: My fellow citizens...
en


"My fellow citizens..."

LineNo: 12402013,

Player_Romus: Great people of Rizia...
en


"Great people of Rizia..."

LineNo: 12402393,

Player_Romus: Servants and the followers of the...
en


"Servants and the followers of the Divine God..."

LineNo: 12402765,

Player_Romus: Citizens of the Divine Sovereignty...
en


"Citizens of the Divine Sovereignty..."

LineNo: 12403423,

Player_Romus: Citizens of the Holy Theocracy...
en


"Citizens of the Holy Theocracy..."

LineNo: 12403525,

Player_Romus: Citizens of the Wruhecist Kingdom...
en


"Citizens of the Wruhecist Kingdom of Rizia..."

LineNo: 12403723,

Player_Romus: As it's tradition, just like my be...
en


"As it's tradition, just like my beloved father and the monarchs before him, I am doing this broadcast to you the people of Rizia."

LineNo: 12403825,

Player_Romus: I am happy to have this opportunit...
en


"I am happy to have this opportunity to talk to you about the current state of affairs in Rizia, as well as its hopeful future."

LineNo: 12403927,

Player_Romus: It is natural that I seem a rather...
en


"It is natural that I seem a rather remote figure to many of you. Someone you only see on television and newspapers. But now for a few minutes, I welcome you to the tranquillity of my home."

LineNo: 12404307,

Player_Romus: It is natural that I seem a rather...
en


"It is natural that I seem a rather remote figure to many of you. Someone far away who never touches your personal lives. But let it be known, my presence will be felt far more directly in your lives from this point forward."

LineNo: 12404679,

Player_Romus: With profound reverence and love,...
en


"With profound reverence and love, I extend my blessings to each of you, my cherished flock, under the watchful eyes of the Divine."

LineNo: 12405187,

Player_Romus: Almost eight years ago, I took the...
en


"Almost eight years ago, I took the throne to serve our Rizia, to bring prosperity to this glorious kingdom."

LineNo: 12405289,

Player_Romus: After my coronation, we faced year...
en


"After my coronation, we faced years of adversity and daunting trials head-on. United, we turned these trials into triumphs."

LineNo: 12405391,

Player_Romus: You demanded more political rights...
en


"You demanded more political rights from the crown, demanded the right to elect your own government. I am now overjoyed to say the crown has given its full attention to you."

LineNo: 12405771,

Player_Romus: You wanted a strong and prosperous...
en


"You wanted a strong and prosperous Rizia, and gave your complete trust in me, your King. To finally bring Rizia glory."

LineNo: 12406263,

Player_Romus: Throughout my reign, I have been u...
en


"Throughout my reign, I have been uplifted and sustained by the knowledge that your thoughts and prayers were with me."

LineNo: 12406365,

Player_Romus: I have always been aware that my p...
en


"I have always been aware that my people were united to support me in the task to which I have now been dedicated with such solemnity."

LineNo: 12406467,

Player_Romus: Though some of us try and tear our...
en


"Though some of us try and tear our kingdom apart, I am still uplifted and sustained by the knowledge that Rizian people's thoughts and prayers are with me."

LineNo: 12406569,

Player_Romus: Today is another landmark because...
en


"Today is another landmark because television has made it possible for many of you to see me in your homes."

LineNo: 12406767,

Narrator: I looked directly into the camera.
en


I looked directly into the camera.

LineNo: 12406869,

Player_Romus: Today, there is much to celebrate,...
en


"Today, there is much to celebrate, to look back and feel proud of ourselves."

LineNo: 12406971,

Player_Romus: Now, I want to remind you of the g...
en


"Now, I want to remind you of the great accomplishments that have occurred during my reign."

LineNo: 12407073,

Player_Romus: When we started on this path, some...
en


"When we started on this path, some did not believe we could take it to the end. We proved them all wrong."

LineNo: 12407453,

Player_Romus: When I started on this path, some...
en


"When I started on this path, some did not believe I could take it to the end. I proved them all wrong."

LineNo: 12408041,

Player_Romus: I promised you victory against Pal...
en


"I promised you victory against Pales, and indeed, the Rizian army prevailed!"

LineNo: 12408143,

Player_Romus: We have finally crushed the rogue...
en


"We have finally crushed the rogue government in Pales and ensured that the Grand Duchy will no longer be a problem."

LineNo: 12408523,

Player_Romus: Almost four years ago, Pales openl...
en


"Almost four years ago, Pales openly attacked our soldiers and tried to occupy our castles... And we made them pay for it."

LineNo: 12408625,

Player_Romus: Almost four years ago, Pales openl...
en


"Almost four years ago, Pales openly attacked our ships including RN Valero, and tried to blockade our gas fields... And we made them pay for it."

LineNo: 12409005,

Player_Romus: Years ago, Pales threatened our ki...
en


"Years ago, Pales threatened our kingdom and tried to steal our access to natural resources. And we made them pay for it."

LineNo: 12409227,

Player_Romus: I salute every men and women who h...
en


"I salute every men and women who have served their duties for the Kingdom and contributed to this great victory."

LineNo: 12409329,

Player_Romus: I am still deeply saddened by all...
en


"I am still deeply saddened by all the lives that were lost during the conflict. Both sides have lost many good people, and this war has shown us the value of unity."

LineNo: 12409431,

Player_Romus: Despite all the suffering we've en...
en


"Despite all the suffering we've endured, faced with the same choice, I would defend our kingdom against the Duchy every time."

LineNo: 12409533,

Player_Romus: I took on the responsibility and a...
en


"I took on the responsibility and assumed direct control of our armies and led them to this victory, which involved a lot of tough decisions."

LineNo: 12409913,

Player_Romus: I thank General Azaro and the Rizi...
en


"I thank General Azaro and the Rizian General Staff who assumed the control of our armies and led them to this victory."

LineNo: 12410811,

Player_Romus: Today, however, we must celebrate...
en


"Today, however, we must celebrate the unification of Pales with Rizia. We have been waiting for this moment for a long time."

LineNo: 12410913,

Player_Romus: As a result, we decided on the com...
en


"As a result, we decided on the complete annexation of the Grand Duchy, unifying back with Rizia."

LineNo: 12411015,

Player_Romus: When I was in Pales, I talked to m...
en


"When I was in Pales, I talked to many Palesians who desired the duchy to be part of Rizia. Now, I'm overjoyed to see us all reunited."

LineNo: 12411117,

Player_Romus: Now, Pales as a separate entity, i...
en


"Now, Pales as a separate entity, is no more! Pales has now been integrated as part of our kingdom, and we will work towards rebuilding the duchy as fast as we can."

LineNo: 12411219,

Player_Romus: Today, however, we must celebrate...
en


"Today, however, we must celebrate the restoration of the cities of Arces and Ziqes to Rizia. We have been waiting for this moment for a long time."

LineNo: 12411321,

Player_Romus: As a result, we decided to annex t...
en


"As a result, we decided to annex the northern territories of the Grand Duchy, which are home to many Rizians, bringing them back home."

LineNo: 12411423,

Player_Romus: When I was in Pales, I talked to m...
en


"When I was in Pales, I talked to many Palesians who desired to be part of Rizia. Now, I'm overjoyed to see northern Pales reunited."

LineNo: 12411525,

Player_Romus: Now, Pales has been divided! Rizia...
en


"Now, Pales has been divided! Rizian parts of Pales have been integrated as part of our kingdom, and we will continue to work closely with the duchy to bring stability to the region."

LineNo: 12411739,

Player_Romus: So, let's take this moment to cele...
en


"So, let's take this moment to celebrate our victory. This is the beginning of the rise of Rizia."

LineNo: 12411841,

Player_Romus: So, let's use this moment to honor...
en


"So, let's use this moment to honor and remember all who died on this journey. We must never forget their sacrifice."

LineNo: 12411943,

Player_Romus: So, let us now look to the future...
en


"So, let us now look to the future with the peace we established."

LineNo: 12412331,

Player_Romus: I am proud to have secured peace w...
en


"I am proud to have secured peace with Pales. Now that the war is over, we will look towards building a better future."

LineNo: 12412711,

Player_Romus: I salute every men and women who h...
en


"I salute every men and women who have served their duties for the Kingdom and contributed to this war."

LineNo: 12413299,

Player_Romus: However, there are also sad develo...
en


"However, there are also sad developments that have recently occurred. Rizia was forced to surrender against our war with the Grand Duchy of Pales."

LineNo: 12413401,

Player_Romus: I must also say that I am deeply s...
en


"I must also say that I am deeply saddened by the events that have occurred in Pales. But I am glad that we could achieve peace in the end."

LineNo: 12413503,

Player_Romus: But before I go on further, I ask...
en


"But before I go on further, I ask the forgiveness of each and everyone of you. I have betrayed your trust with our defeat."

LineNo: 12413725,

Player_Romus: I am still deeply saddened by all...
en


"I am still deeply saddened by all the lives that were lost during the conflict. Both sides have lost many good people, and this war has shown us the value of unity."

LineNo: 12413827,

Player_Romus: Despite all the suffering we've en...
en


"Despite all the suffering we've endured, faced with the same choice, I would defend our kingdom against the Duchy every time."

LineNo: 12413929,

Player_Romus: I salute every men and women who h...
en


"I salute every men and women who have served their duties for the Kingdom and contributed to this war."

LineNo: 12414031,

Player_Romus: Despite not reaching the results w...
en


"Despite not reaching the results we wanted, our intervention into Pales was completely justified."

LineNo: 12414245,

Player_Romus: So, let's take this moment to cele...
en


"So, let's take this moment to celebrate the end of the war. This will be a new beginning."

LineNo: 12414347,

Player_Romus: So, let's use this moment to honor...
en


"So, let's use this moment to honor and remember all who died on this journey. We must never forget their sacrifice."

LineNo: 12414449,

Player_Romus: So, let us now look to the future...
en


"So, let us now look to the future with the peace we established."

LineNo: 12415625,

Player_Romus: However, today there is also much...
en


"However, today there is also much to celebrate, to look back and feel proud of ourselves."

LineNo: 12415727,

Player_Romus: Now, I want to remind you of the g...
en


"Now, I want to remind you of the great accomplishments that have occurred during my reign."

LineNo: 12415829,

Player_Romus: But not everything is so tragic. W...
en


"But not everything is so tragic. We have achievements that will never be forgotten."

LineNo: 12416021,

Player_Romus: Now, I want to talk about some acc...
en


"Now, I want to talk about some accomplishments that have occurred during my reign."

LineNo: 12416513,

Player_Romus: On top of that, despite President...
en


"On top of that, despite President Smolak's best attempts against it, we finally managed to bring Zille back to Rizia."

LineNo: 12416615,

Player_Romus: But of course, there is more to ce...
en


"But of course, there is more to celebrate. Zille agreement is now history. We are reunited with our brothers and sisters once again."

LineNo: 12416717,

Player_Romus: I am also honored to announce the...
en


"I am also honored to announce the return of Zille back to our Kingdom."

LineNo: 12416819,

Player_Romus: Despite President Smolak's best at...
en


"Despite President Smolak's best attempts against it, we finally managed to bring Zille back to Rizia."

LineNo: 12416921,

Player_Romus: Today, Zille agreement is a piece...
en


"Today, Zille agreement is a piece of history. We are reunited with our brothers and sisters once again."

LineNo: 12417023,

Player_Romus: I am honored to announce the retur...
en


"I am honored to announce the return of Zille back to our Kingdom!"

LineNo: 12418215,

Player_Romus: But most importantly, we brought r...
en


"But most importantly, we brought reform to our kingdom."

LineNo: 12418317,

Player_Romus: On top of our successes abroad, we...
en


"On top of our successes abroad, we also accomplished much inside our political system."

LineNo: 12418419,

Player_Romus: Now I want to talk about one of th...
en


"Now I want to talk about one of the biggest of our achievements, which was the declaration of the Rizian Charter of Fundamental Law."

LineNo: 12418521,

Player_Romus: I want to congratulate our parliam...
en


"I want to congratulate our parliament in drafting the new constitution. Together, we brought historic reforms to our kingdom."

LineNo: 12418623,

Player_Romus: By enshrining the separation of po...
en


"By enshrining the separation of powers in a written charter, we have accomplished much inside our political system."

LineNo: 12418725,

Player_Romus: One of the biggest of our achievem...
en


"One of the biggest of our achievements was the declaration of the Rizian Charter of Fundamental Law."

LineNo: 12418827,

Narrator: I took a deep breath.
en


I took a deep breath.

LineNo: 12419917,

Player_Romus: First of all, I want to remind you...
en


"First of all, I want to remind you about our new alliance and the future of Southern Merkopa."

LineNo: 12420019,

Player_Romus: Today, we must celebrate what we h...
en


"Today, we must celebrate what we have accomplished with our neighbors."

LineNo: 12420121,

Player_Romus: I also want to highlight one of my...
en


"I also want to highlight one of my regime's biggest achievements, which was the declaration of the Intermerkopum Alliance."

LineNo: 12420223,

Player_Romus: But that's not all. With the estab...
en


"But that's not all. With the establishment of Intermerkopum, the future of Southern Merkopa is in our hands."

LineNo: 12420325,

Player_Romus: We also recently announced our new...
en


"We also recently announced our new alliance: Intermerkopum."

LineNo: 12420427,

Player_Romus: I also want to highlight another a...
en


"I also want to highlight another achievement of ours. The declaration of the Intermerkopum alliance."

LineNo: 12420625,

Player_Romus: And thus, the Great Unification is...
en


"And thus, the Great Unification is complete."

LineNo: 12420727,

Player_Romus: With both Pales and Zille reunited...
en


"With both Pales and Zille reunited back with the kingdom, we turned back the wheels of time."

LineNo: 12420829,

Player_Romus: And with that, the Rizian peninsul...
en


"And with that, the Rizian peninsula is now completely united under Rizia, once again!"

LineNo: 12420931,

Player_Romus: With the new constitution, we esta...
en


"With the new constitution, we established a new system of democracy, by giving the House of Delegates the law-making power."

LineNo: 12421033,

Player_Romus: In accordance with the new laws, R...
en


"In accordance with the new laws, Rizian laws will be governed solely by the Rizian legislative, which is then governed by a head of government, the Rizian people will soon get a chance to elect."

LineNo: 12421135,

Player_Romus: For the first time ever, I, as a m...
en


"For the first time ever, I, as a monarch, have transferred my law-making powers to the legislative branch."

LineNo: 12421349,

Player_Romus: My father once dreamed of this day...
en


"My father once dreamed of this day of reunification with Pales, and indeed, today that dream has been realized."

LineNo: 12421451,

Player_Romus: The sacred union between my daught...
en


"The sacred union between my daughter and the Duke of Pales has not only blessed our families but has also woven the fabric of our kingdom and the Duchy of Pales into a single, unbreakable entity."

LineNo: 12421553,

Player_Romus: Our reunification with Pales marks...
en


"Our reunification with Pales marks a new chapter, not defined by lineage or title, but by shared aspirations and collective well-being of our people."

LineNo: 12421767,

Player_Romus: This strategic merger with the Duc...
en


"This strategic merger with the Duchy of Pales enhances our kingdom's stature on the global stage, fortifying our borders and expanding our influence."

LineNo: 12421869,

Player_Romus: While we welcome the Palesian regi...
en


"While we welcome the Palesian region, we must navigate this transition with care, ensuring that the integration honors the legacy and desires of all our people."

LineNo: 12421971,

Player_Romus: So let us celebrate our reunion. L...
en


"So let us celebrate our reunion. Let us celebrate what we've been waiting for a very long time."

LineNo: 12422185,

Player_Romus: I wish a great life for Vina and A...
en


"I wish a great life for Vina and Axel in this holy union. May God bless their marriage."

LineNo: 12422287,

Player_Romus: Therefore I'd like to take this mo...
en


"Therefore I'd like to take this moment to congratulate the marriage between Vina Toras and Axel Reinhart."

LineNo: 12422389,

Player_Romus: Glovurius axa Rizia, axa Pales!
en


"Glovurius axa Rizia, axa Pales!"

LineNo: 12422611,

Player_Romus: These reforms represent our commit...
en


"These reforms represent our commitment to democracy, entrusting the voice of the people to shape our kingdom's future."

LineNo: 12422713,

Player_Romus: Though we've shifted lawmaking to...
en


"Though we've shifted lawmaking to Parliament, let us not forget the enduring wisdom of our monarchy, which has guided Rizia through centuries."

LineNo: 12422815,

Player_Romus: By establishing a new head of gove...
en


"By establishing a new head of government, we embrace a future where governance is dynamic, responsive, and, most importantly, reflective of our people's will."

LineNo: 12422917,

Player_Romus: Centralizing our previously semi-a...
en


"Centralizing our previously semi-autonomous regions will strengthen the core of our kingdom, ensuring that our policies and progress are cohesive and uniformly beneficial."

LineNo: 12423019,

Player_Romus: Times of old monarchs who led thei...
en


"Times of old monarchs who led their soldiers on the battlefield are closed. I will not lead you into battle, I will not give you laws or administer justice, but I can do something else. I can give you my heart and my devotion to this peninsula and to all the peoples of our kingdom."

LineNo: 12423623,

Player_Romus: Moreover, the centralization is no...
en


"Moreover, the centralization is not about diminishing regional diversity but about harnessing our collective strength more effectively, making Rizia more resilient against external pressures."

LineNo: 12423725,

Player_Romus: Our new bicameral system is design...
en


"Our new bicameral system is designed for balance and depth in governance, allowing for more thorough debate and consideration of the laws that shape our daily lives."

LineNo: 12424105,

Player_Romus: Our new bicameral system is design...
en


"Our new bicameral system is designed for balance and depth in governance, allowing for more thorough debate and consideration of the laws that shape our daily lives."

LineNo: 12424207,

Player_Romus: I call upon the Rizian people to g...
en


"I call upon the Rizian people to go and vote. The next elections will change the history of Rizia."

LineNo: 12424309,

Player_Romus: The role of the Prime Minister is...
en


"The role of the Prime Minister is to serve as a steward during this transformative period, ensuring that the upcoming elections are conducted with fairness and transparency."

LineNo: 12424411,

Player_Romus: I ask each one of you to give your...
en


"I ask each one of you to give your support to our Prime Minister, who is not just a guardian of transition but a beacon of progress, empowering you to take the reins of your destiny through the ballot box."

LineNo: 12425285,

Player_Romus: I know some people had concerns ab...
en


"I know some people had concerns about the closure of the House of Delegates. The decision was not made out of a desire for control, but to steer our kingdom through turbulent waters with a steady hand, ensuring stability and security for all."

LineNo: 12425387,

Player_Romus: Today, I also want to point out th...
en


"Today, I also want to point out that the suspension of our parliament is a temporary measure, a pause to recalibrate and reform, so that in its rebirth, it may serve our people more effectively and equitably."

LineNo: 12425489,

Player_Romus: History has shown us that a centra...
en


"History has shown us that a centralized monarchy can respond with the decisiveness and unity that fragmented parliamentary systems often lack, ensuring the prosperity and security of our kingdom. That is why I will continue ruling without the House of Delegates."

LineNo: 12425591,

Player_Romus: Let is also be known that the mist...
en


"Let is also be known that the mistake my father made with the foundation of the House of Delegates has been undone and the same mistakes will never be made again."

LineNo: 12426211,

Player_Romus: I stand here with a heavy heart, k...
en


"I stand here with a heavy heart, knowing that we couldn't achieve peace in Pales yet. But we must not falter, it is our duty as Rizians to protect our kingdom and to support our brave soldiers who are giving their lives for our safety."

LineNo: 12426313,

Player_Romus: In this trying times, as we face t...
en


"In this trying times, as we face the challenges of war with Pales, let us not lose sight of our ultimate goal - reconciliation. A future where peace reigns is within our grasp if we extend the olive branch with sincerity and hope."

LineNo: 12426415,

Player_Romus: I ask everyone's patience and unde...
en


"I ask everyone's patience and understanding in these difficult times."

LineNo: 12426517,

Player_Romus: Even as the echoes of war with Pal...
en


"Even as the echoes of war with Pales still reverberate through our kingdom, I assure you, we will be victorious. The enemy will surrender in no time."

LineNo: 12426731,

Player_Romus_Italic: I decided not to mention the war.
en


I decided not to mention the war.

LineNo: 12426737,

Player_Romus_Italic: I decided not to mention the war.
Menu Text en


Don't mention the war.

LineNo: 12426839,

Player_Romus: I promise the Rizian people a swif...
en


"I promise the Rizian people a swift and complete victory of Rizia and ask for your patience."

LineNo: 12426941,

Player_Romus: We are still fired up and ready to...
en


"We are still fired up and ready to take this to the end."

LineNo: 12427139,

Player_Romus: As a founding member of this allia...
en


"As a founding member of this alliance, Rizia will set the pace for the future of our region."

LineNo: 12427241,

Player: By securing valuable international...
en


"By securing valuable international deals, we brought foreign investment and greatly increased our economic prosperity."

LineNo: 12427247,

Player: By securing valuable international...
Menu Text en


"By securing valuable international deals, we brought foreign investment and greatly increased our economic prosperity."

LineNo: 12427881,

Player: We completed one of the biggest in...
en


"We completed one of the biggest infrastructure projects in Sordland's history, which led to rapid economic development."

LineNo: 12427887,

Player: We completed one of the biggest in...
Menu Text en


"We completed one of the biggest infrastructure projects in Sordland's history, which led to rapid economic development."

LineNo: 12427981,

Player_Romus: Together with {RiziaDLCText.Interm...
en


"Together with {RiziaDLCText.IntermerkopumCountries}, we will be walking into the future with more confident steps."

LineNo: 12428083,

Player_Romus: We will stand together with our al...
en


"We will stand together with our allies against any attempts to intervene in our region by the ATO, the CSP or anyone else."

LineNo: 12428185,

Player_Romus: This organization will bring prosp...
en
